 Career History



Chief Executive Officer

                                    2006 - Current                


TCI Contracting LLC


                  TCI Contracting LLC, a subsidiary of Installed Building Products, Inc., is an American company located in Alpharetta, GA, that provides construction products and installation services. It was founded by J. Michael Nixon, he has been the CEO since 2006. TCI Contracting LLC was acquired by Installed Building Products, Inc. on 31 Dec 12.                




Owner

                                    Current                


Hawks Ridge Golf Club LLC


                  Hawks Ridge Golf Club LLC operates as an estate community and private golf club. It features golf training center, on-property cottages, and places for special events such as wedding, birthday, and private golf outings. The company was founded in 1999 and is headquartered in Ball Ground, GA.                




Founder

                                    Prior                


Quality Insulation, Inc.







 Boards & Committees



Corporate Boards ▾




Member, Board of Directors

                    2012 - Current                  


Installed Building Products, Inc.

                    Installed Building Products, Inc. operates as a insulation installer for the residential new construction market and installer of complementary building products, including garage doors, rain gutters, shower doors, closet shelving and mirrors. The company was founded in 1977 and is headquartered in Columbus, OH.                  





