Director of Installed Building Products (NYSE:IBP), Nixon J Michael, sells 12,797 shares worth $639,850
According to Installed Building Products's most recent Form 4 filing with the SEC dated Mar 07 08:21 PM, company Director, Nixon J Michael disclosed selling 12,797 shares at a cost of $50.00. At the time of this transaction (Mar 03), this trade was worth $639,850 in total. As of Mar 03, Nixon J Michael now owns 1,645,917 shares in total worth about $80,485,341.3. 
For the last few recent trades made by Installed Building Products (NYSE:IBP) Director, Nixon J Michael, we have the following information:




SEC Form 4 filing: Mar 01: Sold 6,140 shares at the rate of $50.00 per share. Total worth of this trade was $307,000. Total number of shares owned as of Mar 01 were 1,667,518
SEC Form 4 filing: Mar 02: Sold 8,804 shares at the rate of $50.00 per share. Total worth of this trade was $440,200. Total number of shares owned as of Mar 02 were 1,658,714
