Mission. Upgraded.
The world’s first action sports smartwatch just got smarter. With the release of the Android Wear 2.0 software update, the Mission now offers expanded features for both iPhone and Android users.

Learn More


















Team Designed. Custom Built with a Purpose.
We needed a smartwatch that could keep up with us no matter where our days took us. So we made it. Powered by Android Wear™ and working hand in hand with Surfline and Snocountry, the Mission is equipped with preloaded apps and real-time surf and snow shred alerts right on your wrist so you’ll never-not-know.

Learn More
 Play Video


















Built Tough. Rugged Enough to Go Wherever You go.
With groundbreaking water resistant capabilities, a custom-molded case made from polycarbonate and stainless steel and a 316L grade stainless steel bezel that performs as a roll cage, the Mission is built tough to withstand the elements. Any of them.

Learn More
 Play Video


















Custom. Make it Your Own.
Choose your case finish, custom bezel color, band color, and custom caseback engraving to create your own "1 of 1" Mission.

Learn More
 Play Video


















Mission Control. Your World on Your Wrist.
Built on the latest technology from Google’s Android Wear™ smartwatch platform, the Mission comes preloaded with the Nixon exclusive Mission and Trace apps, bringing your world to your wrist.

Learn More
 Play Video






















Google Fit
Step up your fitness. Google Fit tracks steps, time, distance, and calories to help you measure and achieve your fitness goals.





Google Play™ Music
Use your Bluetooth headphones and listen to downloaded music on your watch without your phone.





Google Maps™
You can speak to your watch to get turn-by-turn directions to your destination. Say your destination, and the route will appear on your watch.





Remote Shutter
You can use your watch as a remote control to take photos with Google Camera on your phone.





Weather
OK Google, do I need an umbrella today? Get the latest weather updates right on your wrist with Google Now.





Flights
Never miss a flight with timely reminders from Google Now on your watch.





will Mission work with my mobile device?
Mission requires a mobile device running Android 4.3+ or iOS 8.2+. Supported features may vary between platforms. Please visit g.co/wearcheck on your Android phone or iPhone® to see if it’s compatible.










